{"tid":1962312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇錦樑串林鄭：而家仲唔夠差咩","createTime":"2020-04-07T11:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T00:57:10.000Z","uid":19552,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1ae6fb82d2afc8d90d81539323513c838a8e493b","tid":1962312,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:38:15.000Z","msg":"立法會特別財會今日討論政府開支預算，期間不論民主及建制陣營均有代表，斥行政長官林鄭月娥繼續加薪不當，要求減薪。商務及經濟發展局前局長蘇錦樑亦在社交平台回應，質疑當局為何還未就市況調整薪酬。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官辦公室常任秘書長林雪麗今日出席會議時，在輪番批評下只表示，問責團隊已在2月時捐出1個月薪金，「如社會情況轉差會適時回應」。蘇錦樑晚上於Facebook發文引述報道時反問：「現在情況不夠差，還要再轉差才回應」？<br />\n<br />\n蘇錦樑曾任民建聯副主席，於2011年至2017年擔任商經局局長，在林鄭月娥履新特首前即離任，現為私募基金Investcorp及東方海外(00316)董事。"},{"pid":"126e5291196d515b33182295c44c9c44934a43c1","tid":1962312,"uid":39092,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"蘇錦樑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75d6b98c5917addc4f0e6caf22e5746ba0ac2ed","tid":1962312,"uid":318069,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:39:24.000Z","msg":"攬炒之母頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9833edb3c64147e62eff72880e96061dad8634d4","tid":1962312,"uid":19552,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"d75d6b98c5917addc4f0e6caf22e5746ba0ac2ed","tid":1962312,"uid":318069,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:39:24.000Z","msg":"攬炒之母頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:40:04.000Z","msg":"民建聯心入面屌鳩林鄭"},{"pid":"9224bf7f46e768edc0660180792603e8028296d7","tid":1962312,"uid":30215,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:41:19.000Z","msg":"在位時又唔見你咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo